		{
			"name": "📁 5. НОВІ SECURITY ТЕСТИ 🛡️",
			"item": [
				{
					"name": "⚠️ Test Rate Limiting (6th request)",
					"request": {
						"method": "POST",
						"header": [
							{
								"key": "Content-Type",
								"value": "application/json"
							}
						],
						"body": {
							"mode": "raw",
							"raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"test.user@gmail.com\",\n  \"password\": \"wrong_password\"\n}"
						},
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{base_url}}/auth/login",
							"host": ["{{base_url}}"],
							"path": ["auth", "login"]
						},
						"description": "🛡️ **НОВИЙ ТЕСТ: ThrottlerGuard Rate Limiting**\n\n**Як тестувати:**\nВиконай цей запит 6 разів поспіль:\n- Перші 5: 401 Unauthorized (wrong password)\n- 6-й запит: 429 Too Many Requests\n\n**Що тестуємо:**\n- ThrottlerGuard на login endpoint\n- Rate limit: 5 спроб за 60 секунд\n- IP-based tracking"
					},
					"response": [],
					"event": [
						{
							"listen": "test",
							"script": {
								"type": "text/javascript",
								"exec": [
									"pm.test('Rate limiting works (401 or 429)', function () {",
									"    pm.expect([401, 429]).to.include(pm.response.code);",
									"});",
									"",
									"if (pm.response.code === 429) {",
									"    pm.test('Rate limit message', function () {",
									"        const jsonData = pm.response.json();",
									"        pm.expect(jsonData.message).to.include('ThrottlerException');",
									"    });",
									"    console.log('🛡️ Rate limiting активний!');",
